From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: robert-brunson-fragile <siinspam@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:20:41 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 02/23] feat(agent): normalize tool call aliases for shorthand
 names

Map shorthand tool names (e.g. "write" -> "write_file", "shell" ->
"terminal") to their canonical names before dispatch. Leaves the alias
in place when the target tool is unavailable. Supports OpenAI-style
tool_call objects and raw dict tool calls.

Co-authored-by: Nako <280596805+nakoagent@users.noreply.github.com>

